@Mr_AlexHall @BrianAraujo9 @Memphis901FC @bhmlegion @MCBrigade14 Yessir! Appropriately shorn. Good danglage. Well executed. 💪
@josephmdurso On the one hand everything about this is shady as hell. On the other I have no choice but to blindly believe our content queen. https://t.co/dcevYA3pDA

@mdb80 I’m not lowering the bar. I said exactly what I meant (on a character-constrained platform). He’s doing everything well except finishing, but you need that out of a 9… so Wright deserves a look (and all the others on the list — Sargent, Dike, Pefok, et al — are still in play)

Sometimes when you win, you really lose. And sometimes when you lose, you really win. And sometimes when you win or lose, you actually tie. And sometimes when you tie, you actually win big because you drop the danglies on LLL Triste.

#b2bwcw #pray4em https://t.co/X0j8EOjzy7

Decent 1H from #UMSNT vs quality opponent. Had some looks. Conceded some chances.

•Love Weah. Dude ALWAYS looking to be dangerous.

•Defense ok. Left big gaps but recovered.

•Ferreira doing everything well — except finish. Hopefully matter of time but Weight deserves look.

I don’t love our group. I LOVE our group.

Wales - 3 points
England - 3 points
Iran - 3 points

Light work. Biggest Q: who finishes 2nd in group A and gets spanked by us in R16?? (Netherlands, Ecuador, Senegal or Qatar)
GARETH BALE IS A BAD MAN AND MORE IMPORTANTLY MIGHT BE THE BAD MAN (WHO BEATS UKRAINE SO WE DONT HAVE TO)
@ryandonovan__ Yeah I’d say that’s an unfortunate oversimplification… but when I showed up the only blogs getting posted about soccer was now the sport itself sucks — progress?!
@mo12822 The Babyjesus has pulled some incredible stuff out… when Tommy the Terrorist plays him

@ksherman1818 @Mr_AlexHall @tombogert @MenInBlazers @ussoccer You basically just made my point. $60 for the cheapest tickets means $250-$300 for a family of 4 just to get in the door. Congrats if that’s not a lot of money to you. It is to a lot of other people who are *consistently* being priced out of games.

@ksherman1818 @Mr_AlexHall @tombogert @MenInBlazers @ussoccer You ain’t breaking new ground if your point is soccer isn’t as popular here as other countries. That’s not the issue. UMSNT is plenty popular to fill a 26K stadium in Cincy on a Wed night… IF the fed prices tickets better. So yes, it is about prices. Exclusively.
From way downtown BANG @SDEibarEN https://t.co/pq6D2xAaLh
@AmericasKopite Disgraceful @UEFA
Dirk Kuyt looks like he could still smoke fools but there is a 0.00000% chance that club is ever going to win anything with that logo. Sorry but facts are facts. https://t.co/HvjVdvyJNA
@MLS Who didn’t?

@CalcioMoneyball Mehhhh depends how rose-colored (or whatever the opposite is) your glasses are. Morocco’s pen was total bullshit. They had some other looks but no more than we did. How Ferreira didn’t score one is beyond me. Just as easily could’ve been 4-0 as 3-2.
@ksherman1818 @tombogert @MenInBlazers @ussoccer That’s precisely what it boils down to
@CalcioMoneyball On paper, for sure

What a game. That is what USMNT is all about. Morocco is solid. We played them off the field — while making wholesale subs. I don’t love this team. I *LOVE* this team.

Now imagine how much fun it would’ve been to watch while rocking this (I know, right?) https://t.co/IVfMNBLR0z
@tombogert @MenInBlazers Love that he brought this up. Bout time someone called @ussoccer out on their pricing strategy. Trying to pinch pennies rather than fill stadiums. Wake tf up.
@PatrickBemis1 🗣TALK TO EM
@Goggs123NK Frustration from getting played off the field
@YAMANSDOOD @John_AJackson Yep
@BarstoolBigCat @AaronRodgers12 @FBI @CIA @DHSgov @PGATOUR @DogBountyHunter @INTERPOL_HQ @ATFHQ Don’t let this distract you from the fact Matt Turner is a golden penalty saving god
Holy hell I didn’t know @delatorreluca had that kind of acceleration. Sheesh. Mans said “beep beep” and sprinted thru Morocco’s midfield… with the damn ball at his feet.
Christian Pulisic hands ball to Haji Wright who slots penalty home. I’m not crine you’re crine. I don’t love this team. I LOVE this team. #b2bwcw #pray4em

Someone please clip that run of play from 54:42 to 55:10 and put it on my gravestone. We won the ball off Morocco at midfield. Passed it back to GK. Then worked it all the way down the field with brilliant tuck and go passes. I love this team. I fucking LOVE this team. #b2bwcw
Can everyone finally just stfu about Turner not being able to play with his feet? Seriously. Stfu. Thanks.
@CopyDoug @MLS_Buzz Who we fighting? Lemme at em!!
GB just confirmed Haji Wright, CCV and Scally will start second half. The haters won’t like hearing it but I don’t have a single criticism of his personnel decisions so far this game.
